    "name": "Regina King",
    "photo": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzkxNTBhNzctOTEzMi00NDc2LWJjZDYtMzBhNmI4MmVlOTZhXkEyXkFqcGc@._V1_.jpg",
    "bio": "Regina King was born in Los Angeles, California, to Gloria, a special education teacher, and Thomas King, an electrician. She began her career in the television show , followed by a role in . She began to be recognized by a mainstream audience after her role as 's character's wife in . She co-starred in as 's character's wife.",
