    "bio": "Born to and Charles Cooper. Gary attended school at Dunstable school England, Helena Montana and Grinnell College, Grinnell, Iowa (then called Iowa College). His first stage experience was during high school and college. Afterwards, he worked as an extra for one year before getting a part in a two-reeler by the independent producer . was his first leading lady. He then appeared in for United Artists before moving to Paramount. While there he appeared in a small part in , , and other films.",
