    "photo": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTcyMTU5MzgxMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTYwMDI0NjI1._V1_.jpg",
    "bio": "Mads Mikkelsen's great successes parallel those achieved by the Danish film industry since the mid-1990s. He was born in Østerbro, Copenhagen, to Bente Christiansen, a nurse, and , a banker.Starting out as a low-life pusher/junkie in the 1996 success , he slowly grew to become one of Denmark's biggest movie actors. The success in his home country includes , and the Emmy-winning police series .His success has taken him abroad where he has played alongside in as well as in the Spanish comedy and the American blockbuster .He played the role of Dr. Hannibal Lecter in the critically acclaimed NBC series , from 2013 to 2015, with great success.",
