    "bio": "Precocious, outspoken child-teen starlet of the 1990s, Christina Ricci was born on February 12, 1980 in Santa Monica, California, the youngest of four children of Sarah (Murdoch), a realtor, and Ralph Ricci, a lawyer and therapist. She is of Italian (from her paternal grandfather), Irish, and Scots-Irish descent. She made her screen debut at the age of 9 in , in which she worked with and . Her breakthrough adult role was in , in which she plays a nymphet who skillfully seduces two brothers. She worked with and in the film .",
